# Welcome on KGen sources

## About KGen technologies

KGen is a Firefox addon. It use XUL and Javascript. You can get more information on the Mozilla Developer Center (https://developper.mozilla.org).

To get KGen for production go there https://addons.mozilla.org/fr/firefox/addon/kgen/ . For the development version, follow the above quick start guide.

More informations on the official web site : http://kgen.elitwork.com

## Quick start

Create a new Firefox profile for add on development (https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Setting_up_extension_development_environment).

Clone the project into the extension folder of this new profile.

-Unix/Linux :
$ git clone git://github.com/nfroidure/KGen.git ~/.mozilla/firefox/(FirefoxProfile)/extensions/kgen@elitwork.com

-Windows sample :
$ git clone git://github.com/nfroidure/KGen.git C:\Documents and Settings\(WindowsProfiles)\Application Data\Mozilla\Firefox\Profiles\(FirefoxProfile)\extensions\kgen@elitwork.com

The extension will be installed on the next Firefox start (with dev. profile). Restart firefox on each changes to test them.

## About locales

DO NOT add or modify locales files! Those are managed in Babelzilla only! http://www.babelzilla.org

Have fun!

